     *----------------------------------------------------------------
     *
     *  ZZGET1   Get record(s) for screen 1.
     *
     C     zzget1        begsr
     *
     *   Get record from main file.
     *
     C                   if        $pcmd = '*VIEW   '
     C     fileky        chain(n)  lrsnrc                             7978
     C                   else
     C     fileky        chain     lrsnrc                             7978
     C                   endif
     *
     *  Record locked.
     *
     C                   if        *in78
     C                   eval      error = '1'
     C                   eval      $prtn = '*PGMQ   '
     C                   exsr      zm74
     C                   goto      endgt2
     C                   endif
     *
     *  Record not found.
     *
     C                   if        *in79
     C                   eval      error = '1'
     C                   eval      $prtn = '*PGMQ   '
     C                   exsr      zm73
     C                   goto      endgt2
     C                   endif
     C     endgt2        endsr
     *----------------------------------------------------------------
     *
