     *   -OR- Update record (it was read and locked in ZZGET2)
     *
     C                   update    lrsnrc                               79
     C                   if        *in79
     C                   eval      error = '1'
     C                   exsr      zm72
     C                   goto      endupd
     C                   endif
     C                   endif
     *
     *   Move key values to parameters
     *
     C                   eval      $prscd = lrscde
